Scope; Partner Sites
This Privacy Policy applies to Personal Information we collect through our Site, App, home security devices and other interactions with you including email and phone. Our Site contains links to partner sites that are not owned or controlled by SimpliSafe. Please be aware that we are not responsible for the privacy practices of these other sites. We encourage you to be aware when you leave our Site and to read the privacy statements of these other sites that collect your Personal Information.
