(such as information about your and your devices’ interaction with our network, your interaction with our Site and App, your visitor identification number, your product usage, the website you navigated from to reach our site, timestamp information about your visit to our site, the pages on our site that you view, including pages visited, your mouse movement and keystrokes for evaluating site functionality, and the name of your internet service provider)
Audio, visual and similar information
(if you use our security cameras or other camera-enabled products, we collect information such as audio and video recordings from such devices so that we can provide the guaranteed services)
Inferences
(such as a profile based on information reflecting your activity and preferences)
Geolocation Information (as necessary to utilize Bluetooth and Wifi functionality of our products and services.
Precise geolocation is only collected in a one-time fashion in order to enable Wifi capabilities, other instances of Geolocation collection are coarse
)
Sensitive Personal Information
(combination of email address and password, or other credentials, such as safeword, allowing access to your account; and protected classification characteristics, if you voluntarily provide them in response to our surveys, such as your race and ethnicity)
Our sources for this Personal Information:
Communications we have with you in any way including in person, by phone, online, by email or text, or by online live chat. Please note that we record and save calls involving our customer service team and any online chats
Your interaction with the Site and the App, both in the form of Personal Information collected automatically and provided directly by you
If you add a Live Guard Protect capable camera and enable this feature,we may collect video recordings and associated audio when a recording is initiated or when you interact with our monitoring agents as part of the Live Guard Protection feature. Find more on Live Guard Protection by visiting our Help Center
We receive this Personal Information directly from you when you purchase, setup and use our products and services, and when you communicate with us
We sometimes combine information that you voluntarily provide to us with information that we automatically collect when you visit our websites or interact with our products and services
We receive this Personal Information from analytics partners and advertising and marketing companies
Our business purposes for collecting this Personal Information:
To deliver our products and services to you, such as our Video Verification and Live Guard Protection features
