California, Virginia, Colorado, Oregon, Texas, Connecticut and Utah residents can use the toggle below to opt out of the “sale” and “sharing” of their personal information as intended by the California Consumer Privacy Act ("CCPA"), the Virginia Consumer Data Protection Act ("VCDPA"), the Colorado Privacy Act ("CPA"), the Oregon Consumer Privacy Act ("OCPA"), the Texas Data Privacy And Security Act ("TDPSA"), the Connecticut Data Privacy Act ("CTDPA") and the Utah Consumer Privacy Act ("UCPA"). We will comply with your request within 15 business days.
As noted in our Privacy Policy, we may “sell” or “share” personal information about you for cross-context behavioral or targeted advertising purposes but will never exchange your personal information for money. For more information on SimpliSafe’s privacy practices and your rights under the CCPA, the VCDPA, the CPA, the CTDPA, the OCPA, the TDPSA and the UCPA visit our
Privacy Policy
.
SimpliSafe does not process personal information of California, Virginia, Connecticut, Colorado, Oregon, Texas or Utah residents for purposes of profiling in furtherance of decisions that produce legal or similarly significant effects.
